<span id="freeTextContainer9769838515345776043">Is it me, or is this eerily similar to Death of A Salesman, if <i>Death</i> were retitled &apos;Linda Loman Has a Morphine Problem&apos;?<br/><br/>(Which is not to say that I didn&apos;t breathlessly read it in one sitting because I was so gripped by it, or that Jamie quoting Swinburne didn&apos;t nearly bring me to tears.)</span>
  <span id="freeText9769838515345776043" style="display:none">Is it me, or is this eerily similar to Death of A Salesman, if <i>Death</i> were retitled 'Linda Loman Has a Morphine Problem'?<br /><br />(Which is not to say that I didn't breathlessly read it in one sitting because I was so gripped by it, or that Jamie quoting Swinburne didn't nearly bring me to tears.)</span>
